```

### ‚úÖ Correct: Using object parameters
```typescript
await whop.companies.listMembers({
  companyId: "biz_123",   // Object-based params
  filters: {
    accessPassIds: ["prod_xxx"]
  }
});
```

### ‚ùå Wrong: Using limited SDK
```typescript
